The project is on MSTest 3.8.0. The user wants to fix the `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj, out var typed)` pattern for MSTest v4.

In MSTest v4, the `out` parameter overload was removed. Instead, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj)` now returns `T` directly. So the fix is:

```csharp
// Before (v3)
Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj, out var typed);

// After (v4)
var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj);
```

Let me update the package version and fix the three assertions.

